@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_erxisv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.cos(wp.cos(tmp + 0.37)))
    v0 = (v0 / v2)
    v2 = 0.88
    v2 = 0.57
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.abs(v2))
    tmp = v0
    v2 = (wp.cos(v2) + wp.exp(v0))
    v0 = 0.49
    data[tid] = v0
